aw Funds from School Account) ..&gt; (Update Logs) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Deposit Funds to School Account) ..&gt; (Update Logs) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n    }\n\n    rectangle \&quot;Students\&quot; {\n        S -- (View Educational Content Dashboard as a Student)\n        S -- (Submit Assignments and Assessments)\n        S -- (Pay School Fees and Other Welfare Fees)\n        S -- (Submit Medicals for Sudden Leaves)\n        S -- (Enter Extracurricular Activity Information)\n        S -- (Create School Societies and Clubs)\n\n        (View Educational Content Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (View Assessments) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (View Educational Content Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (Upload Assessments) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (View Educational Content Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (Update Assessments) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Submit Assignments and Assessments) ..&gt; (Inform Subject Teachers) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Pay School Fees and Other Welfare Fees) ..&gt; (Generate Receipts) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Submit Medicals for Sudden Leaves) ..&gt; (Verify Medical Information) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Enter Extracurricular Activity Information) &lt;.. (Update Information) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Create School Societies and Clubs) &lt;.. (Add Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Create School Societies and Clubs) &lt;.. (Remove Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Create School Societies and Clubs) &lt;.. (Update Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        SP -- (Enter Student Information as a Prefect)\n        SP -- (Create Events for Students)\n        SP -- (Delete Events for Students)\n        SP -- (Update Events for Students)\n\n        (Enter Student Information as a Prefect) &lt;.. (Update Student Information as a Prefect)\n        (Create Events for Students) ..&gt; (Inform Students as a Prefect) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Delete Events f